Lots of learning: another take on Murray during the second session of this 2 week pose. I finished up the first drawing from my previous post early into the session and decided to  try more experiments with #strathmore 400 paper and #charcoal. I'm hoping to find more of balance between how I naturally draw and this longer way of drawing as I experiment with different charcoal and paper combos. #lifedrawingintoronto

Trying out some digital workflows to see if I can stretch my practice a bit. Starting out with #AdobeFresco — I've been having lots of fun with the experience so far. How has your experience with Fresco been versus other drawing apps? I'm hoping still to document my traditional practice and share it at some point 🤞, but this is a start 😁.
